            "text": {
              "status": "generated",
              "div": "<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"><h3>Annotation</h3><table class=\"hl7__eu__lab__report\"><tr><th>Conclusion and Recommendations based on this report and previous findings known to us</th></tr><tr><td>The patient shows mildly elevated HbA1c, indicating suboptimal long-term glycemic control (prediabetes range). All other parameters are within normal limits except for a slightly low total CO₂, which may suggest mild metabolic acidosis or compensated respiratory alkalosis. Renal function and electrolytes are normal. Recommend clinical correlation and monitoring of glycemic status.</td></tr></table></div>"
